                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>ἐπὶ Τιμοδ<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/><orig>Τ</orig><gap reason="illegible" unit="character" quantity="1"/><orig>Ω</orig><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/> ὁ δᾶμος <choice><sic>το͂ν</sic><corr>τῶν</corr></choice> <choice><corr>Γελώιων</corr><sic>Γελόιον</sic></choice>.
                </ab>
